for(i in 1:(length(weekday)-1)){

    }

}

base_rec_lunch <- train %>% 
  recipe(~.) %>% 
  step_mutate(=---,
                    =/,
                    =/,
                    =/,
                    =/,
                    =/,
                    =year(),
                    =month(),
                    =day(),
  ) %>% 
  step_rm(,,,,,
               ,) %>% 
  prep()


train_base_lunch <- base_rec_lunch %>% juice()
test_base_lunch <- bake(base_rec_lunch,test) #   NA ?

train_base_lunch<-train_base_lunch %>% mutate(holiday= factor(holiday))

set.seed(125)
rf_mod <- 
  rand_forest() %>% 
  set_mode("regression") %>% 
  set_engine("ranger", importance = 'impurity') 
#importance = "impurity" , "permutation"  vip() 
rf_wf <- 
  workflow() %>% 
  add_model(rf_mod) %>% 
  add_formula(~.)
rf_fit <- rf_wf %>% 
  fit(train_base_lunch)


rf_wf2 <- 
  workflow() %>% 
  add_model(rf_mod) %>% 
  add_formula(~.)
rf_fit2 <- rf_wf2 %>% 
  fit(train_base_dinner)

#   - vip()
# 
rf_fit %>% 
  pull_workflow_fit() %>% 
  vip(num_features = 30)

# 
rf_fit2%>% 
  pull_workflow_fit() %>% 
  vip(num_features = 30)

rf_pred1 <- predict(rf_fit, new_data = test_base_lunch) 

rf_pred2 <- predict(rf_fit2, new_data = test_base_dinner) 

sample_submission$<-rf_pred1$.pred
sample_submission$<-rf_pred2$.pred



write.csv(sample_submission,"basemodel.csv",row.names = F,fileEncoding = "UTF-8")
